title: Stem cells provide greater insight into rotator cuff disease

title_detail.value: Stem cells provide greater insight into rotator cuff disease

summary: New research explores stem cells in the rotator cuff in hopes of understanding why fatty accumulation happens at the tear site, instead of proper muscle healing.
